summary: Keesha. pretty Redguard - Starting in Helgen before the Dragon attacks...
descriptionHtml:
I created a pretty redguard and decided to share the savegame with you. There is an optional save near the three stones, \"Stone of Thief\" is already activated. Ran through Helgen with Ralof, just for your information.

Just extract and add to your \"Saves\", usually located at C:\\User\\xyz\\My Documents\\My Games\\Skyrim\\.
Maybe you need to rename the files to fit your order of savegames.

Have fun :)
author: Scrypher
